WEBVTT

00:10.905 --> 00:14.207
Probably a lot of different deaths,
a lot of violent deaths.

00:14.209 --> 00:17.177
It just seems like it's
getting worse for everyone.

00:17.179 --> 00:19.579
He says, "Those [bleep] got to go."

00:19.581 --> 00:21.715
He shoots himself with the same rifle

00:21.717 --> 00:23.250
that killed his stepdaughter.

00:23.252 --> 00:24.835
That's a twist.

00:24.837 --> 00:27.621
Someone said, "That's the room of death."

00:27.623 --> 00:30.624
My son whispered, he says,
"That's a bad guy."

00:30.626 --> 00:32.392
Would you say they're a threat?

00:33.528 --> 00:38.198
Something wiped everybody out.

00:38.200 --> 00:40.867
"You're mine. You can't escape."

00:40.869 --> 00:43.270
My name is Amy Allan.

00:43.272 --> 00:46.173
What's happening?

00:46.175 --> 00:47.274
I see dead people.

00:47.276 --> 00:49.709
It seems like a devil.

00:49.711 --> 00:51.411
I speak to dead people.

00:51.413 --> 00:53.079
He's pissed off.

00:53.081 --> 00:54.514
And they speak to me.

00:54.516 --> 00:56.149
I felt real fear.

00:56.151 --> 00:59.619
But there's only one way to
know if my findings are real.

00:59.621 --> 01:01.188
I think she's being murdered.

01:01.190 --> 01:02.511
I rely on my partner.

01:02.711 --> 01:04.328
I'm Steve Di Schiavi.

01:04.330 --> 01:05.996
I'm a retired New York
City homicide detective.

01:05.998 --> 01:07.731
Serial killer pops in my head.

01:07.733 --> 01:11.301
And I know every person,
every house has secrets.

01:11.303 --> 01:12.502
Nobody believes me.

01:12.504 --> 01:13.937
It's my job to reveal them.

01:13.939 --> 01:16.239
- Do you think there's still bodies there?
- I do.

01:16.241 --> 01:17.974
But Steve and I never speak...

01:17.976 --> 01:20.010
We never communicate
during an investigation.

01:20.012 --> 01:21.211
...until the very end.

01:21.213 --> 01:22.879
You got problems. I got news for you.

01:22.881 --> 01:25.165
When we uncover if it's
safe for you to stay...

01:25.167 --> 01:27.250
This is our house...
whether they like it or not.

01:27.252 --> 01:28.518
Or time to get out.

01:28.520 --> 01:31.588
This is their house, the house of the dead.

